metadata.name: CT Friends - @notsofast
metadata.description:
This track is part of the CT Friends Series in which I rip the voices of my favorite Crypto Twitter avatars from interviews or podcasts and produce original songs with them.

In addition, I create a card-a-like animated video with a specific theme for each one.

Only 9 "@notsofast" minted!

IMPORTANT: This preview is a watermarked lo-fi (audio/video) version of the original media!
Purchase will unlock access to a High Quality 1080x810 320 kbps MP4 file without the watermark. 

The NFT holder is granted a CC Licence (Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International)

Big Thanks to @notsofast
